    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. looking at the data though, a lot of economists are saying that the supply-side arguments don't really hold up in a modern economy compared to the progressive models. do you think the bill is actually going to work as intended, or is the idea that it stimulates growth just a way to justify the wealth gap?",
